column10: would set FYbudget for 1978 in September 1977, in September 1978, would set FYbudget for 1979

**Republicans became majority party in Senate following inauguration of Bush in Jan 2001. BUT then in June 2001, an independent Senator switched from Rep to Ind and transferring control to Democrats, then was back to Republicans by November 2002…so actually should be Democrat when the vote happened, but Republican for the next year (2003 vote for 2004 budget)
